				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/07/10/16042-ces-bobos-qui-reclament-la-liberte-de-non-reflexion?replytocom=81779#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-81779", "81779", "respond", "16042")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
