	<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 comment-item">
		<article id="comment-81888" class="comment-block">
			<header class="comment-header">
				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/8d0dca1ea813e5b692eeef1e9f2f6d7d?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">					<a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.carveboard.fr">raphael</a>
